            <fr:title text="Forester 4.0">Forester 4.0</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Release</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>This is a major release of Forester that changes both the command line interface <fr:em>and</fr:em> the XML format, introducing many new features under the hood as well as quality-of-life improvements (including a 2X rendering speedup).</fr:p>
